dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning districts for Kenosha County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Kenosha_Zoning_2018.gdb. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are NKenosha_General_2018N and NKenosha_Shoreland_2018N. [Kenosha County Zoning Districts.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Kenosha County Planning and Development Department
